---
title: Creamy Bacon and Ricotta Pasta with Parmesan and Peas
description: Inspired by the perfect Roman pasta - carbonara - this penne dish features rich bacon and a silky ricotta sauce. Sweet green peas burst in each bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-bacon-and-ricotta-pasta-6ab43f44.jpg
